<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>CAE-PRESS enables designers to perform a stress analysis through seamless operations of CAD and CAE.<br>Designers are only required to perform simple CAD input operations without being concerned with CAE.</p><p><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered"><strong>Features</strong></h2><h3>The &quot;StressAnalysis&quot; command</h3><hr><p>Stress analyses can be performed through simple input operations.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/02.CAE-PRESS/CAE_PRESS_01.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>The &quot;StressAnalysis&quot; command</h3><hr><p>It is possible to display and output quickly the results that have been saved after the execution of the command for stress analysis.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/02.CAE-PRESS/CAE_PRESS_02.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p><br></p><h3>The &#39;DieDeflectionAnalysis&#39; command</h3><hr><p>The load information output when the product panel is analyzed by the forming analysis software is read and analyzed as input conditions.<br><br></p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/CB9981E7-6AB2-D8CC-FD0F-2F2069D16147.jpeg" width="285" height="270" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3 class="fr-text-bordered">Inquiries</h3><p>If you have any inquiries about our product or would like to request a visit to your place for explanation or demonstration, please use the inquiry form.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/contact"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Contact Us &rarr;</span></a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" ti